General Assembly House Joint
Resolution No. 5
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 1732
Referred to Committee on JUDICIARY
Introduced by:
(JUD)
RESOLUTION CONFIRMING THE CLAIMS COMMISSIONER'S
COMPENSATION AWARD TO CHARLES WILLIAMS WITH RESPECT
TO HIS CLAIM AGAINST THE STATE FOR WRONGFUL
INCARCERATION.
Resolved by this Assembly:
1 That the decision of the Claims Commissioner, file number 27161 of
2 said commissioner, that compensation in the amount of $2,237,901.68,
3 payable from the adjudicated claims account of the General Fund, be
4 awarded to Charles Williams with respect to his claim against the state
5 for wrongful incarceration, is confirmed.
LCO No. 1732 1 of 1

